<p class="greeting">Hi there!</p>

<p>Someone has requested a link to reset your password for your Prep-2-Plate account. You can do this by clicking the button below.</p>

<table class="body-action" align="center" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" role="presentation">
  <tr>
    <td align="center">
      <%= link_to 'Reset My Password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), class: 'button', target: '_blank' %>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p>If you didn't request this password reset, please ignore this email. Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>

<table class="body-sub" role="presentation">
  <tr>
    <td>
      <p class="f-fallback sub">If you're having trouble with the button above, copy and paste the URL below into your web browser.</p>
      <p class="f-fallback sub"><%= edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %></p>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
